  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help your team of robot co-workers clear the scrap in this fast-paced match-3 game. Good performance unlocks new robots with unique block-stacking patterns and styles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514390/extras/075c7cb018367d8a73dbeb7e884273fb.poster.avif?t=1732999571\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514390/extras/075c7cb018367d8a73dbeb7e884273fb.webm?t=1732999571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514390/extras/075c7cb018367d8a73dbeb7e884273fb.mp4?t=1732999571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four (4) robots violating their original operating parameters for fun and profit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 accessibility options, including separate music and SFX sliders</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 achievements for pro players to show off their skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Integrated tutorial to teach you the basics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficulty options and advanced tips for expert players </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High score list to track your best times and scores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable using only the mouse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playable using only the keyboard</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >XBox and PlayStation controllers supported via Community Layouts (no UI prompt support)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Deck supported using either buttons or touchscreen (no UI prompt support)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Native Linux and Steam Deck support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision cursor option for touchscreens</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extremely realistic CRT display (note: not very realistic)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Extremely realistic Einsteinian wormhole physics (note: dangerously realistic)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pre-rendered CGI animations will make you check you haven't time traveled back to the 90s</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At least one cheat code</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514390/extras/74c49b1ab5360dc8c55f4dfcb0771f0e.poster.avif?t=1732999571\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514390/extras/74c49b1ab5360dc8c55f4dfcb0771f0e.webm?t=1732999571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514390/extras/74c49b1ab5360dc8c55f4dfcb0771f0e.mp4?t=1732999571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes accessibility options for improved visibility and reduced distractions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514390/extras/1a479e8caf6d3d540bccce8a2adf8dcb.avif?t=1732999571\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2514390/extras_big/1a479e8caf6d3d540bccce8a2adf8dcb.avif?t=1732999571 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
